          </span>
        </div>
        <h1
          class="fd-hero__title"
        >
          Dashain
        </h1>
        <p
          class="fd-hero__nepali text-nepali"
        >
          दशैं
        </p>
        <p
          class="fd-hero__summary"
        >
          Blessing, reunion, and seasonal turning gathered into one long observance.
        </p>
        <div
          class="fd-hero__actions"
        >
          <button
            class="btn btn-primary btn-sm"
            type="button"
          >
            Save
          </button>
          <button
            class="btn btn-secondary btn-sm"
            type="button"
          >
            Remind me
          </button>
          <button
            class="btn btn-secondary btn-sm"
            type="button"
          >
            Share
          </button>
        </div>
        <div
          class="fd-hero__facts"
        >
          <article
            class="fd-hero__fact"
          >
            <span>
              Calendar
            </span>
            <strong>
              Lunisolar profile
            </strong>
          </article>
          <article
            class="fd-hero__fact"
          >
            <span>
              Duration
            </span>
            <strong>
              10 days
            </strong>
          </article>
          <article
            class="fd-hero__fact"
          >
            <span>
              Profile
            </span>
            <strong>
              computed
            </strong>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div
        class="fd-hero__side"
      >
        <article
          class="fd-seal-card"
        >
          <div
            aria-hidden="true"
            class="fd-seal-card__art"
          >
            <svg
              class="fd-seal-card__svg"
              viewBox="0 0 120 120"
            >
              <circle
                class="fd-seal-card__ring fd-seal-card__ring--outer"
                cx="60"
                cy="60"
                r="44"
              />
              <circle
                class="fd-seal-card__ring fd-seal-card__ring--inner"
                cx="60"
                cy="60"
                r="28"
              />
              <path
                class="fd-seal-card__petal"
                d="M60 26 L70 60 L60 94 L50 60 Z"
              />
              <path
                class="fd-seal-card__petal fd-seal-card__petal--soft"
                d="M26 60 L60 70 L94 60 L60 50 Z"
              />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <span
            class="fd-seal-card__eyebrow"
          >
            Festival seal
          </span>
          <strong>
            Shared civic rhythm
          </strong>
          <p>
            This observance next appears on October 20, 2026 and stays visible in the rolling festival calendar for the coming years.
          </p>
        </article>
        <article
          class="fd-date-card"
        >
          <span
            class="fd-countdown fd-countdown--future"
          >
            219 days away
          </span>
          <strong>
            October 20, 2026
          </strong>
          <small>
            October 30, 2026 end
          </small>
          <div
            class="fd-date-card__row"
          >
            <span>
              Bikram Sambat
            </span>
            <span>
              2083 Ashwin 4
               - 2083 Ashwin 14
            </span>
          </div>
          <div
            class="fd-date-card__row"
          >
            <span>
              Method
            </span>
            <span>
              lunisolar festival profile
            </span>
          </div>
          <div
            class="fd-date-card__actions"
          >
            <button
              class="btn btn-secondary btn-sm"
              type="button"
            >
              Add to calendar
            </button>
            <button
              class="btn btn-secondary btn-sm"
              type="button"
            >
              Future years
            </button>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </header>
    <div
      class="fd-layout"
    >
      <div
        class="fd-main"
      >
        <article
          class="ink-card fd-story"
        >
          <div
            class="fd-section-head"
          >
            <div>
              <p
                class="today-page__eyebrow"
              >
                Meaning
              </p>
              <h2>
                Why it matters
              </h2>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p>
            Dashain gathers family, blessing, and renewal into the largest festival rhythm in Nepal.
          </p>
          <p>
            The observance is commonly tied to the victory of Durga over disorder and the renewal of protective strength.
          </p>
          <div
            class="fd-story__highlight"
          >
            <span>
              Context
            </span>
            <strong>
              Families mark the season through blessing, homecoming, and ritual continuity across generations.
            </strong>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article
          class="ink-card fd-practice"
        >
          <div
            class="fd-section-head"
          >
            <div>
              <p
                class="today-page__eyebrow"
              >
                Observance
              </p>
              <h2>
                How it is practiced
              </h2>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div
            class="fd-practice__list"
          >
            <article
              class="fd-practice__item"
            >
              <span
                class="fd-practice__index"
              >
                01
              </span>
              <div
                class="fd-practice__content"
              >
                <h3>
                  Ghatasthapana
                </h3>
                <p>
                  The observance begins by establishing sacred space and invoking protective presence.
                </p>
                <ul
                  class="fd-practice__events"
                >
                  <li>
                    <strong>
                      Kalash Sthapana
                    </strong>
                    <span>
                      A ritual vessel and barley planting begin the seasonal sequence.
                    </span>
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </article>
            <article
              class="fd-practice__item"
            >
              <span
                class="fd-practice__index"
              >
                02
              </span>
              <div
                class="fd-practice__content"
              >
                <h3>
                  Maha Ashtami
                </h3>
                <p>
                  The household rhythm intensifies around worship, preparation, and offering.
                </p>
                <ul
                  class="fd-practice__events"
                >
                  <li>
                    <strong>
                      Durga Puja
                    </strong>
                    <span>
                      Families and temples observe the fierce protecting form of the goddess.
                    </span>
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </article>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article
          class="ink-card fd-rhythm"
          id="future-years"
        >
          <div
            class="fd-section-head"
          >
            <div>
              <p
                class="today-page__eyebrow"
              >
                Date rhythm
              </p>
              <h2>
                How the observance moves over time
              </h2>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p
            class="fd-rhythm__intro"
          >
            This observance next appears on October 20, 2026 and stays visible in the rolling festival calendar for the coming years.
          </p>
          <div
            class="fd-rhythm__rows"
          >
            <article
